{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be bold and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Bold EdTech</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #d32f2f; /* Bold Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e57373; /* Lighter Red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #212121; /* Dark background */\n            --accent-color: #f44336; /* Brighter Red for accents */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            min-height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features h3 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #181818;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Bold EdTech</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ignite Your Learning Journey</h2>\n            <p>Experience education like never before. Our platform offers cutting-edge courses and tools designed to empower you to achieve your goals. Boldly embrace the future of learning.</p>\n            <a href=\"#features\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Courses</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>What Makes Us Bold</h3>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h4>Interactive Lessons</h4>\n                    <p>Engage with dynamic content and hands-on activities that bring complex subjects to life.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h4>Expert Instructors</h4>\n                    <p>Learn from industry leaders and seasoned professionals who share their real-world expertise.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h4>Personalized Paths</h4>\n                    <p>Tailor your learning experience with adaptive technology that adjusts to your pace and style.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h4>Community Driven</h4>\n                    <p>Connect with a global network of learners and instructors to collaborate and grow.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Bold EdTech. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}